{"tid":1224424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好比我批死 建制派遲啲又會撐返修例","createTime":"2019-06-15T03:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T07:25:06.000Z","uid":912,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2e24f3219cc4ae3aaef85a41636c2b311e6c29b7","tid":1224424,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:23:33.000Z","msg":"各位<br />\n暫緩唔係撒回<br />\n星期一二係空左立法會<br />\n隨時可以開返會<br />\n建制派仍然都係講緊「解說不足」<br />\n啲19高官吹到啲人搞事 影響啲人搵食<br />\n宜家仲係好落力捉人<br />\n教育局又嚇9啲教師<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好比我批死！<br />\n改少少不痛不癢嘅細節<br />\n就話聽咗市民意見<br />\n建制派又會出返黎撐修例<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">616一定要出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n團結一心<br />\n不撒不散<br />\n不放不散<br />\n追究到底"},{"pid":"fc973f84884e5f82af1dcdaf382ed948d3ee42a1","tid":1224424,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:24:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdd1fe01f92b610f3ec067fbbc15a7094cf231d","tid":1224424,"uid":111898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"最多咪拖到過左選舉再支持<br />\n今次除左要撤回 追究 落台 仲要vote them out"},{"pid":"e6ddc719c5588905322b3fd2116b5512d6844e13","tid":1224424,"uid":912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:27:06.000Z","msg":"一定要傳出去<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府冇諗過收手</span>"},{"pid":"8c716b85a22ccd5f28f7bd8f74af9d2ec8e5682d","tid":1224424,"uid":912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2bdd1fe01f92b610f3ec067fbbc15a7094cf231d","tid":1224424,"uid":111898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"最多咪拖到過左選舉再支持<br />\n今次除左要撤回 追究 落台 仲要vote them out"},"citedBy":0,"reply